			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				the best use for befriend/charm animal has not been given, so i will explain.<BR>
<BR>
elephants and mammys have an insane radius for keeping aggro.  it is the entire zone.  you can aggro them as pets.<BR>
<BR>
by typing, '/pet attack quillmane'; if quillmane is up in the entire zone; the elephant will go after it.  same with, '/pet attack a glacier bear'<BR>
<BR>
on a pvp server, you can check an unknown players team by, '/pet attack playername', and the pet will take off, or tell you that is not a legal target.<BR>
<BR>
i keep a list of all the rare spawns in South Karanas and when i am there; i charm an elephant and start typing.  
				</font>
			</td>

